700566f-a.title: Bronx: Broadway - 238th Street
700566f-a.text:
Broadway (left), south from W. 238th Street, showing the
elevated structure of the II.R.T. subway line thereon. On the
rimht is Kingsbridge Avenue, running south from its commencement
point at W. 238th Street.
September 28, 1913
Gift of M. Vaxer
MAY BE REPRODUCED
